'''Dark Side Squadron''' was the designation used by the [[Dark Side Elite]] of the [[Dark Empire]] during at least one mission<ref name="DE II audio">[[Dark Empire II (audio drama)|''Dark Empire II'' audio drama]]</ref> in [[10 ABY/Legends|10 ABY]].<ref name="Death date">''[[The New Essential Chronology]]'' dates the events of [[Dark Empire II (audio drama)|''Dark Empire II'' audio drama]], which features the [[Battle of New Alderaan (Operation Shadow Hand)|battle of New Alderaan]], to [[10 ABY/Legends|10 ABY]].</ref> Piloting [[I-7 Howlrunner]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]], the group participated in a [[Battle of New Alderaan (Operation Shadow Hand)|raid]] on [[New Alderaan/Legends|New Alderaan]] to abduct [[Darth Caedus|Jacen]] and [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]]. They were defeated by [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], [[Kam Solusar]] and [[Empatojayos Brand]]. The leader of the group, [[Executor (Imperial rank)|Executor]] [[Xecr Nist]], led Dark Side Squadron as well, flying under the callsign [[Dark Side One]].<ref name="DE II audio" />

